replies.body:
Tear Rain, which comes with downloading osu!, is a good start.

Aoi Eir- IGNITE is a popular and decently simple beatmap to play. I like to play it with Hard Rock. Heh, SAO hype.

sakuzyo- Black Lair is a good song to teach recovery from spinners.

There are many good songs out there, whether easy, normal, hard, or even harder; you just have to search. Remember, practice makes perfect!

Oh, and whatever you do, do not do what I did, which was download some of the hardest songs to start off (My first two downloaded songs were The Big Black and FREEDOM DiVE lol). That's also the reason I have only a 30% accuracy; I've done too many hard songs on No-Fail.
